@model MyAngularW3V1_02042018.RouteConfig

@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Index";
}
<script src="~/scripts/angular.min.js"></script>
<h2>Index</h2>

<div ng-app="" ng-init="myCol='#80bfff'; heroName='Batman'; realName='Bruce Wayne'" >

    <input style="background-color:{{myCol}}" ng-bind="heroName" value="{{heroName}}" />


</div>

<p>AngularJS resolves the expression and returns the result.</p>

<p>The background color of the input box will be whatever you write in the input field.</p>